#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:16
msgid "Chroma Key: Advanced"
msgstr "Croma: avançat"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:18
#| msgid ""
#| "This effect is a more advanced version of the :ref:`Chroma Key: Basic "
#| "<effects-chroma_key_basic>` effect. *Chroma Key: Advanced* [1]_ allows "
#| "for some basic feathering (by changing the :guilabel:`Edge Mode`) and "
#| "much more fine-grained control over how much and in which way you remove "
#| "the background."
msgid ""
"This effect is a more advanced version of the :ref:`Chroma Key: Basic "
"<effects-chroma_key_basic>` effect. *Chroma Key: Advanced*\\ [1]_ allows for "
"some basic feathering (by changing the :guilabel:`Edge Mode`) and much more "
"fine-grained control over how much and in which way you remove the "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Aquest efecte és una versió més avançada de l'efecte :ref:`Croma: bàsic "
"<effects-chroma_key_basic>`. *Croma: avançat*\\ [1]_ permet una mica de "
"difuminat (canviant el :guilabel:`Mode de vora`) i un control molt més fi "
"sobre quant i de quina manera eliminar el fons."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:20
msgid ""
"This is better for backgrounds that have less contrast with the foreground "
"or for more complex backgrounds. For simple (uniform) backgrounds (such as "
"green, blue, red or possibly black), use the :ref:`Chroma Key: Basic "
"<effects-chroma_key_basic>` effect."
msgstr ""
"Aquest és millor per als fons que tenen menys contrast amb el primer pla o "
"fons més complexos. Per a fons (uniformes) senzills (com el verd, blau, "
"vermell o possiblement negre), utilitzeu l'efecte :ref:`Croma: bàsic "
"<effects-chroma_key_basic>`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:24
msgid "Basic Technique"
msgstr "Tècnica bàsica"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:26
msgid ""
"Find a clip with a background (preferably multiple, or slightly complex, "
"because the :ref:`Chroma Key: Basic <effects-chroma_key_basic>` effect can "
"do easy backgrounds such as green or blue). Add the *Chroma Key: Advanced* "
"effect to the clip."
msgstr ""
"Trobeu un clip amb un fons (preferiblement múltiple o lleugerament complex, "
"perquè l'efecte :ref:`Croma: bàsic <effects-chroma_key_basic>` pot fer fons "
"fàcils com el verd o el blau). Afegiu l'efecte *Croma: avançat* al clip."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:28
msgid ""
"Now either choose the color using the color palette by clicking on the "
"colored bar. Or use the little pipette button and then click in the Project "
"Monitor on the background part of the clip you want to remove. Adjust the :"
"guilabel:`Delta` sliders until the background is removed correctly. This "
"might need some experimenting. If you find it is not removing the background "
"well try changing the :guilabel:`Color Model` and experiment again. If you "
"experimented and cycled through all the :guilabel:`Color Models`, and the "
"background is still not removed properly then it is probably too complicated "
"for **Kdenlive** to remove. At this point, you will most likely need to use :"
"ref:`Rotoscoping <effects-rotoscoping>`."
msgstr ""
"Ara trieu el color utilitzant la paleta de colors fent clic a la barra de "
"colors. O utilitzeu el botó de pipeta petita i feu clic a la part del fons "
"del clip que voleu eliminar al monitor del projecte. Ajusteu els controls "
"lliscants de :guilabel:`Delta` fins que el fons s'elimini correctament. Això "
"podria necessitar alguna prova. Si trobeu que no està eliminant bé el fons, "
"proveu de canviar el :guilabel:`Model de color` i experimenteu de nou. Si "
"heu experimentat i heu passat a través de tots els :guilabel:`Models de "
"color`, i el fons encara no s'ha eliminat correctament, probablement serà "
"massa complicat que el **Kdenlive** l'elimini. En aquest punt, probablement "
"haureu d'utilitzar :ref:`Rotoscòpia <effects-rotoscoping>`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/alpha_mask_keying/chroma_key_advanced.rst:30
msgid ""
"If the effect took lots of time to experiment, and you want to use this "
"effect again, then click on the |document-save|:guilabel:`Save effect` icon. "
"Give the effect a name and a comment and click on :guilabel:`Ok`. Your "
"custom *Chroma Key: Advanced* effect will be saved in the *Custom* effect "
"category from where you can use it just like any other effect."
msgstr ""
"Si l'efecte triga molt de temps en les proves, i voleu tornar a utilitzar "
"aquest efecte, després feu clic a la icona |document-save|:guilabel:`Desa "
"l'efecte`. Doneu un nom i un comentari a l'efecte i feu clic a :guilabel:"
"`D'acord`. L'efecte personalitzat de *Croma: avançat* es desarà a la "
"categoria d'efectes *Personalitzats* des d'on podreu utilitzar-lo com "
"qualsevol altre efecte."

